snippet: Branislav Ivanovic scored with an injury time header to give Chelsea a 2-1 win over Benfica in the Europa League final in Amsterdam and secure the club’s second European title.
abstract: Chelsea defeats Benfica, 2-1, in Europa League final to secure the soccer club's second European title in two seasons after winning the Champions League in 2012.
lead_paragraph: Branislav Ivanovic scored with an injury time header to give Chelsea a 2-1 win over Benfica in the Europa League final in Amsterdam and secure the club’s second European title.
